name: Cubechain
description: Cubechain is a new generation blockchain with processing 24 transantion pools parallel creating 24 data blocks and 3 special blocks forming Cubes. 3 special blocks are 1) Statistics Block 2) Index Block and 3) Escrow Block. These three special blocks provide fast data analysis, search, and scalable payment pervices. With 24 transaction pool running parallel, transaction speed of Cubechain is over 7,000 TPS in Mainnet (over 12,000 TPS in test net).
